  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 55f8968ff7bf14a74b702a9c01b62d8b, type: 3}
  m_Name: '[Ritsu] Search for Note - 3'
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Master.Scripts.DialogueSystem.Conversation
  lines:
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0f3d5344370414927bfd06128770b263, type: 2}
    text: "He took it? And she didn't realize it smelled like a gym bag? You\u2019re
      a legend."
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c0b6716d4b3ae41488323461179cf4a7, type: 2}
    text: She's not happy, Ritsu. But yeah, the job's done. Now, about that pizza
      money...
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0f3d5344370414927bfd06128770b263, type: 2}
    text: "Right, right. Here\u2019s the credit card. Don\u2019t spend it all at
      the vending machine."
